	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm doubtful that a typical hardware store will carry screws of this size, these are tiny.  I don't know where my jar of NES screws is right now, or I'd get a measurement.  Your best bet may be to remove one from a less important cart.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
